text.text: Nice place, Nice people,, very friendly Bharat bhai, I must thank you for tea on closed Saturday of Ahwa. Be aware that last Saturday  Ahwa market will be totally closed even now tea stall will be open. Very nice view and locality.

text.text: Thank you so much Bharat bhai and Sharmila jiüôè It's the best place to stay at Ahwa. It's a homestay with the feel of home. We stayed there for a few weeks. Their home is ideally situated, just around the famous sunset point. I enjoy photography, and got a few amazing shots of the sunset and surrounding nature. The cherry on top is that the owners are really caring and loving. The rooms are airy, beautiful, clean, and with an attached bathroom. I'll always remember this place. It was a wonderful stay. Thank you again üôèüôè
